    --~~ Kii ~~--
    
    A Rails powered wiki with a codebase that hasn't
    drowned itself in a toilet.
    
    Work in progress!
    
    
    --~~ Setup ~~--
    
    Download the files.
    
    Run `git submodule init` and `git submodule update`.
    
    Run `rake kii:install`.
    
    Finished!